d de Jesus\n* [[Angelika Dela Cruz]] as Geneva \"Gengen\" Ferrer-Takahashi<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iljf0XxwxTQ |title=Ika-6 na Utos: Geneva is coming |date=June 20, 2017 |publisher=GMA Network |accessdate=September 2, 2017}}</ref> \n* Jacob Briz as Austin de Jesus Fuentabella\n\n;Guest cast\n* [[Karel Marquez]] as Lara Salcedo-Fuentabella<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYhuDEsOHFY |title=Ika-6 na Utos: Rome\u2019s tragic past |date=December 5, 2016 |publisher=GMA Network|accessdate=September 2, 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Lito Legaspi]] as Allan\n* Toby Alejar as Orlando\n* Anna Marin as Anita<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G6_qVXHBv8A |title=Ika-6 na Utos: Nakaw na halik |date=December 15, 2016 |publisher=GMA Network |accessdate=September 3, 2017}}</ref>\n* Marcus Madrigal as Dave\n* Sheila Marie Rodriguez as Cynthia\n* [[Allan Paule]] as Danilo\n* [[Luane Dy]] as a television host \n* Aprilyn Gustillo as Grace\n* [[Zoren Legaspi]] as Lyon Muller\n* [[Chynna Ortaleza]] as Maui Alcaraz\n* [[Leanne Bautista]] as Chelsea Muller\n* Lharby Policarpio as Morgan\n* [[Vince Gamad]] as Darwin\n* [[Elle Ramirez]] as Kenya\n* Marnie Lapuz as Chona\n* [[Bryan Benedict]] as Nato\n* Ranty Portento as Brian Santiago<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CfZBHk6HgVE |title=Ika-6 na Utos: Pagtuklas ni Emma sa katotohanan |date=July 12, 2017 |publisher=GMA Network |accessdate=September 2, 2017}}</ref>\n* [[SexBomb Girls#Former members|Izzy Trazona-Aragon]] as Alberta Alcaraz-Muller\n\n==Ratings==\nAccording to [[AGB Nielsen Philippines]]' Nationwide Urban Television Audience Measurement, the pilot episode of ''Ika-6 na Utos'' earned an\n11.9% rating.<ref>{{cite web|title=AGB: 10 Top-rating Pilot and Finale Daytime episodes in 2016 |author=Ching, Mark Angelo |date=January 1, 2017 |url=https://www.pep.ph/guide/tv/25268/agb-10-top-rating-pilot-and-finale-daytime-shows-in-2016 |accessdate=January 24, 2018}}</ref> While the final episode scored an 8.6% rating.<ref>{{cite web|title=AGB RATINGS: GMA-7 nearly sweeps daytime block |url=https://www.pep.ph/guide/tv/27817/agb-ratings-gma-7-nearly-sweeps-daytime-block |date=April 25, 2018 |accessdate=June 4, 2018}}</ref> The series had its highest rating on people in television homes on July 28, 2017 with a 10.7% rating.<ref>{{Cite web|title=July 28 (Fri) TV Ratings / AGB Nielsen / NUTAM (Afternoon). |url=http://www.pep.ph/news/pepalerts/read/20782 |accessdate=July 28, 2017}}</ref> Based from Television Audience Measurement audience shares among people in television home, the series had its highest rating on February 16, 2018 with a 57.5% rating.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ika-6 na utos got groundbreaking rating in afternoon show according to AGB Nielsen Phils.(TAM) |url=https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1822942097756935&id=509798835737941 |accessdate=March 19, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Accolades==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Accolades received by ''Ika-6 na Utos''\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Recipient\n! Result\n! Ref.\n|-\n| rowspan=13 | 2017\n| rowspan= 3 | 7th OFW Gawad Parangal\n| Best Actress\n| [[Sunshine Dizon]]\n| {{Won}}\n| rowspan= 3 | \n<ref>http://www.gmanetwork.com/entertainment/showbiznews/news/35422/sunshine-dizon-gabby-concepcion-at-wowowin-ilan-sa-pinarangalan-sa-7th-ofw-gawad-parangal/story</ref>\n|-\n| Best Actor\n| [[Gabby Concepcion]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actress\n| [[Ryza Cenon]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Gawad Amerika Awards\n| Most Outstanding Filipino Actress in TV\n| Sunshine Dizon\n| {{Won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=WATCH: Sunshine Dizon, tatanggap ng Best Actress Award sa Amerika para sa 'Ika-6 Na Utos' |url=https://www.gmanetwork.com/entertainment/tv/ika_6_na_utos/35270/watch-sunshine-dizon-tatanggap-ng-best-actress-award-sa-amerika-para-sa-ika-6-na-utos/story |website=gmanetwork.com |accessdate=November 16, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan= 4 | [[31st PMPC Star Awards for Television]]\n| Best Daytime Drama 